{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/aws/aws_index/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"adf6370b-2502-5c74-bded-9c1dbad0be79","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>해당 문서에 설치 방법은 “Redhat 8.4”버전에서 진행하였습니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"관련-document\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-document\" aria-label=\"관련 document permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>관련 Document</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/install-nvidia-driver.html\">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/install-nvidia-driver.html</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/optimize_gpu.html\">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/optimize_gpu.html</a></p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>G타입은 인스턴스 생성하기 전 vCPU 리밋해제가 필요하다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>M,C등 타입과 다르게 Service Quotas에서 Running On-Demand G and VT instances 리밋 해제</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>g4dn 인스턴스 타입은 서울 리전 가용 영역 중 ap-northeast-2b  의 경우 간혹 인스턴스 생성이 안되는 경우가 있다고 한다. (시도하다보면 자리나서 생성 가능하다고 함)</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>보통의 경우 그래픽 드라이버가 설치 된 AMI 이미지 사용하면 되지만 요구사항으로 인해 특정 버전만 사용하는 경우 수동 설치 해야함</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-그래픽-드라이버-설치-전-package-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EC%A0%84-package-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 그래픽 드라이버 설치 전 package 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 그래픽 드라이버 설치 전 Package 설치</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-1-display-code-classlanguage-textconfigurationcode-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-1-display-code-classlanguage-textconfigurationcode-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"1 1 display code classlanguage textconfigurationcode 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-1. display <code class=\"language-text\">configuration</code> 확인</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">configuration:latency=0</code>이 아닌 <code class=\"language-text\">nouveau</code> 포함되어 있다면 <code class=\"language-text\">BlockList</code> 등록 필요</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">#lshw는 기본적으로 설치되어 있지만 없다면 아래 명령어로 설치\n#sudo yum install lshw \n\nlshw -numeric -C display\n\n[sysadmin@ip-10-200-1-172 ~]$ lshw -numeric -C display\nWARNING: you should run this program as super-user.\n  *-display:0 UNCLAIMED\n       ~~~~\n  *-display:1\n       description: 3D controller\n       product: TU104GL [Tesla T4] [10DE:1EB8]\n       vendor: NVIDIA Corporation [10DE]\n       physical id: 1e\n       bus info: pci@0000:00:1e.0\n       version: a1\n       width: 64 bits\n       clock: 33MHz\n       capabilities: bus_master cap_list\n       configuration:latency=0 #&lt;&lt; 이 부분이 nouveau 포함되어 있다면 \"disable 필요\" \n       resources: iomemory:40-3f iomemory:40-3f irq:10 memory:fd000000-fdffffff memory:440000000-44fffffff memory:450000000-451ffffff</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">#nouveau driver disable 방법\n\n1. /etc/default/grep 수정\n---\nsudo vi /etc/default/grub\n\nGRUB_TIMEOUT=1\nGRUB_DISTRIBUTOR=\"$(sed 's, release .*$,,g' /etc/system-release)\"\nGRUB_DEFAULT=saved\nGRUB_DISABLE_SUBMENU=true\nGRUB_TERMINAL_OUTPUT=\"console\"\nGRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX=\"console=ttyS0,115200n8 console=tty0 net.ifnames=0 rd.blacklist=nouveau nvme_core.io_timeout=4294967295 crashkernel=auto\"\nGRUB_DISABLE_RECOVERY=\"true\"\nGRUB_ENABLE_BLSCFG=true\n---\n\nGRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX구분\"console=ttyS~~\" 안 끝에 noveau.modeset=0추가 </code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"1-2-그래픽-드라이버-설치-전에-필요한-패키지-code-classlanguage-textyum-installcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-2-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-code-classlanguage-textyum-installcode\" aria-label=\"1 2 그래픽 드라이버 설치 전에 필요한 패키지 code classlanguage textyum installcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-2. 그래픽 드라이버 설치 전에 필요한 패키지 <code class=\"language-text\">yum install</code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo yum install gcc -y\nsudo yum install perl -y\nsudo yum install kernel-headers -y\nsudo yum install vulkan-loader -y\nsudo yum install pkg-config xorg-dev -y\nsudo yum group install -y \"Development Tools\"\nsudo yum install kernel-devel-$(uname -r) kernel-headers-$(uname -r)</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"1-3-xorg-server-중지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-3-xorg-server-%EC%A4%91%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"1 3 xorg server 중지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-3. Xorg server 중지</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>xorg를 중지하지 않으면 설치 진행 안됨</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo systemctl isolate multi-user.target</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-그래픽-드라이버-다운로드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"2 그래픽 드라이버 다운로드 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 그래픽 드라이버 다운로드</h2>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-nvidia-그래픽-드라이버-다운로드-센터\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-1-nvidia-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C-%EC%84%BC%ED%84%B0\" aria-label=\"2 1 nvidia 그래픽 드라이버 다운로드 센터 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-1. NVIDIA 그래픽 드라이버 다운로드 센터</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Product Type, Series</code>등 인스턴스가 지원하는 드라이버 타입에 맞춰 설정 후 다운로드\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/625b20ae-6283-448e-98bc-1bb5bb2d2b15/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">wget https://us.download.nvidia.com/tesla/525.85.12/NVIDIA-Linux-x86_64-525.85.12.run</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"3 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 설치</h2>\n<h3 id=\"3-1-다운로드-받은-code-classlanguage-textnvidia-linux-runcode-파일-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-1-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%9B%EC%9D%80-code-classlanguage-textnvidia-linux-runcode-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"3 1 다운로드 받은 code classlanguage textnvidia linux runcode 파일 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-1. 다운로드 받은 <code class=\"language-text\">NVIDIA-Linux-*.run</code> 파일 실행</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo sh NVIDIA-Linux-x86_64-525.85.12.run</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>실행하게 되면 로딩 이후 아래와 같은 화면이 나오는데 긍정적(Yes, Ok 등)인 말만 선택해서 진행하도록 하자</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/f9f8598c-13bf-4814-8217-f2ef99f20b7f/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-2-설치-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-2-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"3 2 설치 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-2. 설치 확인</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nvidia-smi\n\n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| NVIDIA-SMI 525.85.12    Driver Version: 525.85.12    CUDA Version: 12.0     |\n|-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n| GPU  Name        Persistence-M| Bus-Id        Disp.A | Volatile Uncorr. ECC |\n| Fan  Temp  Perf  Pwr:Usage/Cap|         Memory-Usage | GPU-Util  Compute M. |\n|                               |                      |               MIG M. |\n|===============================+======================+======================|\n|   0  Tesla T4            Off  | 00000000:00:1E.0 Off |                    0 |\n| N/A   56C    P0    28W /  70W |      2MiB / 15360MiB |      0%      Default |\n|                               |                      |                  N/A |\n+-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n\n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Processes:                                                                  |\n|  GPU   GI   CI        PID   Type   Process name                  GPU Memory |\n|        ID   ID                                                   Usage      |\n|=============================================================================|\n|  No running processes found                                                 |\n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-document\">관련 Document</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EC%A0%84-package-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">1. 그래픽 드라이버 설치 전 Package 설치</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-1-display-configuration-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\">1-1. display <code class=\"language-text\">configuration</code> 확인</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-2-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-yum-install\">1-2. 그래픽 드라이버 설치 전에 필요한 패키지 <code class=\"language-text\">yum install</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-3-xorg-server-%EC%A4%91%EC%A7%80\">1-3. Xorg server 중지</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C\">2. 그래픽 드라이버 다운로드</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#2-1-nvidia-%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD-%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%84-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C-%EC%84%BC%ED%84%B0\">2-1. NVIDIA 그래픽 드라이버 다운로드 센터</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#3-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">3. 설치</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#3-1-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%9B%EC%9D%80-nvidia-linux-run-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\">3-1. 다운로드 받은 <code class=\"language-text\">NVIDIA-Linux-*.run</code> 파일 실행</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-2-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\">3-2. 설치 확인</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"해당 문서에 설치 방법은 “Redhat 8.4”버전에서 진행하였습니다. 관련 Document https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/install-nvidia-driver.html https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/optimize_gpu.html G타입은 인스턴스 생성하기 전 vCPU 리밋해제가 필요하다. M,C등 타입과 다르게 Service Quotas에서 Running On-Demand G and VT instances 리밋 해제 g4dn 인스턴스 타입은 서울 리전 가용 영역 중 ap-northeast-2b  의 경우 간혹 인스턴스 생성이 안되는 경우가 있다고 한다. (시도하다보면 자리나서 생성 가능하다고 함) 보통의 경우 그래픽 드라이버가 설치 된 AMI 이미지 사용하면 되지만 요구사항으로 인해 특정 버전만 사용하는 경우 수동 설치 해야함 1.…","frontmatter":{"date":"August 27, 2023","title":"AWS EC2 인스턴스에 Nvidia Driver 설치하기","categories":"AWS","author":"정욱현","emoji":"😀"},"fields":{"slug":"/aws/aws_index/"}},"next":{"id":"7410b51b-0558-5a5a-9ce9-22c363995ee2","html":"<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/99667634-0642-4cd2-9f44-9019bb0b7a3e/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-steampipe\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-steampipe\" aria-label=\"1 steampipe permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Steampipe?</h2>\n<p>Steampipe는 클라우드 리소스들을 <code class=\"language-text\">DB Query</code> 형태로 조회 할 수 있고 Steampipe도 마찬가지로 여러 CSP 서비스들(AWS,GCP,Azure 등)에서도 사용이 가능하다.</p>\n<p>Steampipe는 <code class=\"language-text\">gRPC</code> 형태로 메시지를 각 <code class=\"language-text\">Plugin</code>을 이용해 클라우드와 통신을 하기에 속도가 빠른 장점이 있다!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/6ec34275-f57a-4276-b73b-0f8a356a43a0/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-일단-사용해보자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%9D%BC%EB%8B%A8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EB%B3%B4%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"2 일단 사용해보자 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 일단 사용해보자!</h2>\n<p>직접 Query문를 실행해보고 경험하지 않으면 자세히 모르니 일단 설치하고 실행해보자!!</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-steampipe-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-1-steampipe-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 1 steampipe 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-1. Steampipe 설치</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Steampipe Install Docs : <a href=\"https://steampipe.io/downloads\">https://steampipe.io/downloads</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"2-2-linux-os-환경의-install\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-2-linux-os-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EC%9D%98-install\" aria-label=\"2 2 linux os 환경의 install permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-2. Linux OS 환경의 Install</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Steampipe Install</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo /bin/sh -c \"$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/turbot/steampipe/main/install.sh)\"\n</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Steampipe AWS Plugin Install</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ steampip plugin install aws</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"2-3-aws-configure-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-3-aws-configure-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"2 3 aws configure 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-3. AWS Configure 설정</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">steampipe</code>사용하기 전에 <code class=\"language-text\">aws configure</code> 설정을 하자</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>사용할 IAM Key는 ReadOnlyAccess Policy를 가지고 있는 Key를 사용하자!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"2-4-query-해보기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-4-query-%ED%95%B4%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2 4 query 해보기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-4. Query 해보기</h3>\n<p>생성한 <code class=\"language-text\">VPC Name Tag</code>를 가져와보자!</p>\n<p>먼저 <code class=\"language-text\">steampipe query</code> 에 접속을 하고 쓸수 있는 <code class=\"language-text\">tables</code> 목록을 보자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ steampipe query\n\n> .tables\n==> aws</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/fa103279-a925-40c5-81f5-9cd6a052502f/image.png\" alt=\"\">\n<code class=\"language-text\">steampipe query</code>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">.tables</code> 명령어를 치면 <code class=\"language-text\">AWS Table</code>를 확인 할 수 있다.\n이 <code class=\"language-text\">Table</code>를 활용해서 VPC 목록을 조회해보자!</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-5-inspect-tables-name\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-5-inspect-tables-name\" aria-label=\"2 5 inspect tables name permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-5. .inspect [Tables Name]</h3>\n<p>아래 명령을 사용하면 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_vpc</code>에서 사용가능한 <code class=\"language-text\">column</code> 확인이 가능하다!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.inspect aws_vpc\t\t\t\t</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/a653822d-cb7a-4aec-aba6-1c3f54f43f8f/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">column</code>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">type</code>별로 표현형태가 다르다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>예로, account_id는 text 형태이지만, tags는 json 형태다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"2-6-select-column-from-table\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-6-select-column-from-table\" aria-label=\"2 6 select column from table permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-6. select [column] from [table]</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">select\n\ttags\nfrom\n\taws_vpc</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/7e66961f-ce59-4125-8417-45827b85c972/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-6-instance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-6-instance\" aria-label=\"2 6 instance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-6. Instance</h3>\n<p>생성된 EC2의 <code class=\"language-text\">ID</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Type</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">IP</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Tags</code>를 가져와보자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">> select \n\tinstance_id,\n\tinstance_type,\n\tprivate_ip_address,tags \nfrom \n\taws_ec2_instance</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/e542d3c4-47f5-4b63-b82d-cbc15c0aa886/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-특정-type-값만-가져오기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-type-%EA%B0%92%EB%A7%8C-%EA%B0%80%EC%A0%B8%EC%98%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"3 특정 type 값만 가져오기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 특정 Type 값만 가져오기</h2>\n<p>EC2의 <code class=\"language-text\">Type</code>값을 가지고 있는 목록 불러와보자!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">> select \n\tinstance_id,\n\tinstance_type,\n\tprivate_ip_address,\n\ttags \nfrom \n\taws_ec2_instance \nwhere \n\tinstance_type='c5.xlarge'</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/jtret2424/post/fbfa2487-1181-4864-9dee-7c60c41c2bc3/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-steampipe\">1. Steampipe?</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-%EC%9D%BC%EB%8B%A8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EB%B3%B4%EC%9E%90\">2. 일단 사용해보자!</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-1-steampipe-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">2-1. Steampipe 설치</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#2-2-linux-os-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EC%9D%98-install\">2-2. Linux OS 환경의 Install</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-3-aws-configure-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">2-3. AWS Configure 설정</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-4-query-%ED%95%B4%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\">2-4. Query 해보기</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-5-inspect-tables-name\">2-5. .inspect [Tables Name]</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-6-select-column-from-table\">2-6. select [column] from [table]</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-6-instance\">2-6. Instance</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#3-%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-type-%EA%B0%92%EB%A7%8C-%EA%B0%80%EC%A0%B8%EC%98%A4%EA%B8%B0\">3. 특정 Type 값만 가져오기</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"August 26, 2023","title":"AWS Resource Management \"Steampipe\" Tool 활용하기","categories":"Tech","author":"정욱현","emoji":"😀"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/steampipe/"}},"prev":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://loafer-wock.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/aws/aws_index/","nextSlug":"/tech/steampipe/","prevSlug":""}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}